**Mafia** | Mafia Team Group
__Basics__
Mafia is the group of the mafia team. Here the team can discuss at night who to kill.
__Members__
Mafioso
Godfather
Framer
Lawyer
Roleblocker

__Formalized__
Unique Group
Passive Start Night: Process: Apply `MafiaExecutor` to @(Role:Mafioso)->RandomPlayer [Condition: @(Role:Mafioso)->Count > 0]
Passive Start Night: Process: Apply `MafiaExecutor` to @(Group:Mafia)->RandomPlayer [Condition: @(Role:Mafioso)->Count is 0]
Passive Start Day:
  • Lock @Self
  • Reveal `The channel has been locked for the day!` to @Self
Passive Start Night:
  • Unlock @Self
  • Reveal `$phname has begun, the channel has been unlocked!` to @Self
